resources.string:
"Ikhulisa okuqukethwe kwesikrini."

"Chofoza isithonjana sokukhulisa ukuze ukhanyise ukukhulisa. Uma uthinta isikrini, isikhulisi sizolandela umunwe wakho. Yeka ukuthinta isikrini ukuze uphume ekukhuliseni."

"Cindezela futhi ubambe isithonjana sesikhulisi ukuze ushintshe indawo yesikhulisi esikrinini."

"Ukuze ushintshe ukukhanya phakathi kokukhulisa, bona Ikhasi lezilungiselelo."
"Uxolo, idivayisi yakho okwamanje ayisekeli isilondolozi-sikrini."\n\n"Sicela ukhubaze isevisi."
